Malice:
 
The remainder of their journey passed by in a blur, all he really noticed was how content and peaceful he was with Wolfblade now.  But soon they reached the coordinates, and stood under a tree to wait.
 
"Where do you want to go first?"

Dark Mouse <raccoon7679@...> wrote:
Wolfblade::

She smiled at him."I love you too much. You asked me to stay, and I
did."  She moved to walk closer to him, so she could lean her head on
his shoulder as they walked. Not exactly a practical form of
locomotion, but a romantic one none the less. She let a dreamy sigh
escape as she walked with him.  


"HA!  Is that all you got?  You boasted such power, such skill!  Where is your power and skill now?  You disappoint me, ha ha ha haa!"
